<br>
- We plan on holding open raids every Saturday and Sunday, 2PM EST.  There will be some midweek open raids as well, usually evenings.<br>
<br>
- Our raid targets will be Epic encounters and Plane Raids. These include:<br>
<br>
Kedge (Phinny)<br>
General (Rogue Epic)<br>
Plane of Growth<br>
Plane of Hate<br>
Plane of Fear<br>
The Hole<br>
Kael (not really either epic or planar, but they're fun!)<br>
Chardok<br>
CoM<br>
<br>
Other targets depending on how things go, possibly Plane of Air or PoP zones.<br>
<br>
<br>
Since the Shards of Chaos has already been successful in raiding the majority of these locations already, I feel confident that these will result in success, and lots of fun and goodwill thrown in (or chaos and darkness if you're evil aligned - we don't discourage any race/class from coming).<br>
<br>
Joint guild raids can be set up too if there are any guilds that are interested.  Guild officers and leaders can contact me in-game or on the SoC website.<br>
<br>
